data.title: Board of Directors
data.text:
Current role Chair of the Board and partner in Persson Invest.

Previous professional experience Group Chief Executive Officer AB Persson Invest.

Other board positions Member of the Board of RELOG AS, Engcon AB and Persson Norge AS.

Education Economics, Umeå University.

Independence Independent of the company and in relation to owners

Shareholding in Diös Fastigheter 350,000 directly owned shares. 22,074,488 shares through part-ownership in AB Persson Invest.

Current role Head of Investments, CIO, of Areims Nordic Investment team and is a member of the Investment Committee

Previous professional experience She has worked in the real estate industry since 2000 and has been active in the Nordic transaction market since the beginning of her career. She was CIO at Castellum and has also been a partner at Tenzing AB. Prior to that she worked at JLL Cross Boarder Team in London and Newsec.

Other board positions Board member of Genova AB and Magnolia AB.

Education MSc in Real Estate and Economics from the Royal Institute of Technology in Stockholm

Independence Independent of the company and its owners

Shareholding in Diös Fastigheter 0

Current role Commercial Property Manager, Diös

Previous professional experience Has been active in the real estate industry since 2001 as a lessor, real estate agent, appraiser, real estate agent and now manager. Previous employers include Inmobiliaria Cielo Group in Los Boliches, Viva Estates in Marbella, Svensk Fastighetsförmedling in Östersund.

Other board positions Chairman of the board of Fastighetsbolaget Norkom.

Education Bachelor's degree, Economics and real estate technology program with focus on Real Estate Brokerage at the University of Gävle.

Independence Dependent in relation to the Company but not to its owners

Shareholding in Diös Fastigheter 1200 directly owned shares.
